6. g++

7. pip3

8. pip3 install sqlalchemy

9. pip3 install pysqlite3

10. git

11. qbittorent

12. sudo apt-get install idle3

13. sudo apt-get install clementine (music player)

14. Jetbrains Toolbox

15. PyCharm Professional, IntelliJ Ultimate, CLion. All through Toolbox

16. Java SDK using Tim Buchalka's video

17. xampp

18. postman (https://www.getpostman.com/)  [Folder should be in: ~/NotInstalledApps and change the downloaded folder name to Postman]

19. mongodb (SAME PROCEDURE FOR MAC) (OPTIONAL: Comes in MEAN Stack installation(bookmarked), Make/Edit scripts accordingly: mongodb_enable, mongodb_start) 
   (https://www.mongodb.com/download-center/v2/community)  [Folder should be in: ~/NotInstalledApps and change the downloaded folder name to mongo]

20. nodejs (OPTIONAL: Comes in MEAN Stack installation) [Download from here: https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager/]

21. npm install -g express  (OPTIONAL: Comes in MEAN Stack installation)

22. angular   (OPTIONAL: Comes in MEAN Stack installation)  download from official website.

23. Installing PHP:
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get upgrade
	sudo apt-get install php
	// Check for version: php -v
	sudo apt-get install php7.2-cgi     // if version is 7.2

	Configuring PHPStorm:
	set path in php interpreter: /usr/bin/php7.2   if version is 7.2
	Select appropriate interpreters

24. Blender, download and paste in ~/NotInsatlledApps : To run it- open the "blender" execuatable

25. Scilab, paste in ~/NotInsatlledApps : TO run it- open "bin/scilab" executable in the folder.

26. GIMP: GNU Image Manipulation Program...   URL:  https://www.gimp.org/downloads/

27. Docker: Sort of a virtual box image.  https://www.howtoforge.com/tutorial/ubuntu-docker/
